                     <interp inst="t18400511-1522-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18400511-1522-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing, on the 22nd of April, 2 breast-pins and chain, value 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18400511-name-1074" type="victimName">
